Iron Wealth Managers Multi Family Office FZCO (Iron Wealth) has received the approval of Dubai World Trade Centre Authority (DWTC) and Government of Dubai to provide multi-family office services to its clients. Iron Wealth becomes the first investment advisory firm in Sub-Saharan Africa to secure this licence from the United Arab Emirates regulator. According to Yemi Adunola, a Director of the company, “this marks an important milestone and will help connect Africa-based High Net Worth Individuals (HNIs), family businesses and family offices to investment opportunities in a global financial hub.” Iron Wealth will focus on providing wealth management and investment advisory services to Africa-based HNIs, family offices and businesses. Iron Wealth is a subsidiary of Iron Capital Partners Limited (Iron Capital). 